Introduction

ChoCo1&2 is a pre-debut co-ed group under ChoCo Entertainment.

Some of the trainees have debuted with the Full Album ChoCo Takes Hollywood (MAX).

They share trainees activities through their Instagram, TikTok, Twitter, and YouTube accounts. Currently, the company is planning to debut two groups; Choco1 for male trainees and Choco2 for female trainees.
